{"sn11.20:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 11.20 ","sn11.20:0.2":"2. Dutiyavagga ","sn11.20:0.3":"Sanghavandanasutta ","sn11.20:1.1":"Savatthiyam jetavane. ","sn11.20:1.2":"Tatra kho …pe… etadavoca: ","sn11.20:1.3":"“bhutapubbam, bhikkhave, sakko devanamindo matalim sangahakam amantesi: ","sn11.20:1.4":"‘yojehi, samma matali, sahassayuttam ajannaratham, uyyanabhumim gacchama subhumim dassanaya’ti. ","sn11.20:1.5":"‘Evam, bhaddantava’ti kho, bhikkhave, matali sangahako sakkassa devanamindassa patissutva, sahassayuttam ajannaratham yojetva sakkassa devanamindassa pativedesi: ","sn11.20:1.6":"‘yutto kho te, marisa, sahassayutto ajannaratho, ","sn11.20:1.7":"yassadani kalam mannasi’ti. ","sn11.20:1.8":"Atha kho, bhikkhave, sakko devanamindo vejayantapasada orohanto anjalim katva sudam bhikkhusangham namassati. ","sn11.20:1.9":"Atha kho, bhikkhave, matali sangahako sakkam devanamindam gathaya ajjhabhasi: ","sn11.20:2.1":"‘Tanhi ete namasseyyum, ","sn11.20:2.2":"putidehasaya nara; ","sn11.20:2.3":"Nimugga kunapamhete, ","sn11.20:2.4":"khuppipasasamappita. ","sn11.20:3.1":"Kim nu tesam pihayasi, ","sn11.20:3.2":"anagarana vasava; ","sn11.20:3.3":"Acaram isinam bruhi, ","sn11.20:3.4":"tam sunoma vaco tava’ti. ","sn11.20:4.1":"‘Etam tesam pihayami, ","sn11.20:4.2":"anagarana matali; ","sn11.20:4.3":"Yamha gama pakkamanti, ","sn11.20:4.4":"anapekkha vajanti te. ","sn11.20:5.1":"Na tesam kotthe openti, ","sn11.20:5.2":"na kumbhi na kalopiyam; ","sn11.20:5.3":"Paranitthitamesana, ","sn11.20:5.4":"tena yapenti subbata. ","sn11.20:6.1":"Sumantamantino dhira, ","sn11.20:6.2":"tunhibhuta samancara; ","sn11.20:6.3":"Deva viruddha asurehi, ","sn11.20:6.4":"puthu macca ca matali. ","sn11.20:7.1":"Aviruddha viruddhesu, ","sn11.20:7.2":"attadandesu nibbuta; ","sn11.20:7.3":"Sadanesu anadana, ","sn11.20:7.4":"te namassami matali’ti. ","sn11.20:8.1":"‘Settha hi kira lokasmim, ","sn11.20:8.2":"ye tvam sakka namassasi; ","sn11.20:8.3":"Ahampi te namassami, ","sn11.20:8.4":"ye namassasi vasava’”ti. ","sn11.20:9.1":"Idam vatvana maghava, ","sn11.20:9.2":"devaraja sujampati; ","sn11.20:9.3":"Bhikkhusangham namassitva, ","sn11.20:9.4":"pamukho rathamaruhiti. ","sn11.20:9.5":"Dutiyo vaggo. ","sn11.20:10.0":"Tassuddanam ","sn11.20:10.1":"Deva pana tayo vutta, ","sn11.20:10.2":"daliddanca ramaneyyakam; ","sn11.20:10.3":"Yajamananca vandana, ","sn11.20:10.4":"tayo sakkanamassanati. "}